    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 then take your <strong>chicken </strong>out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Add your <strong>chicken thighs </strong>to a baking tray (use <strong>tin foil </strong>to avoid mess!) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong> and put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
