    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mushrooms are browned, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, transfer the <strong>mushrooms </strong>to a<strong> food processor </strong>with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Blitz until smooth – this is your<strong> mushroom pâté</strong></p>",
