    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>cooked chicken </strong>to a clean board (reserve the tray!) and shred apart using two forks – this is your <strong>pulled chicken</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>red chilli relish</strong> and <strong>pulled chicken</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and mix until well coated – this is your <strong>sweet chilli chicken</strong></p><p>Discard the <strong>tin foil</strong> from the reserved tray, then add your <strong>baguette[s]</strong> and put the tray in the oven for 2-3 min or until warmed through and crusty</p>",
